properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters from  Suwannee River to Keaton Beach out 20 NM; Coastal waters from Okaloosa-Walton County Line to Mexico Beach out 20 NM; Coastal Waters From  Ochlockonee River to Apalachicola FL out to 20 Nm; Apalachee Bay or Coastal Waters From Keaton Beach to Ochlockonee River Fl out to 20 Nm; Coastal Waters from Mexico Beach to Apalachicola out 20 NM
properties.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued January 15 at 8:52PM EST until January 16 at 1:00PM EST by NWS Tallahassee FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...Dense fog will reduce visibility to one mile or less.

* WHERE...Okaloosa/Walton county line to the Suwannee River out to
20 nautical miles.

* WHEN...Until 1 PM EST /noon CST/ Thursday.

* IMPACTS...Low visibility will make navigation difficult.
properties.instruction:
If you must navigate, proceed with caution. Use proper fog
signals. Make sure all running lights are on. Remember to use
your radar and compass.

NWSheadline: DENSE FOG ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 1 PM EST /NOON CST/ THURSDAY
